casebody.data:
H.F., Petitioner-Movant,
v.
BOARD OF EDUCATION OF the TOWNSHIP OF TEANECK, Respondent-Respondent. M-375/376/377/378/379 September Term 2018
080011 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 6, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-375), to file an overlength brief (M-376), and to file a reply brief (M-379) are granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motions for leave to present oral argument (M-378) and for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the motion for leave to appeal (M-377) are denied.
